    en: "In our youth, we open our eyes wide to the world, tasting life\u2019s sweetness while also enduring the bitterness of growing up. The fiction in this unit involves adolescent growth or observes the world from a young person\u2019s perspective. Study this unit to learn to trace plot, analyze characters from different angles, and understand themes."
